data.description: Beautifully Remodeled Ranch, with an all open floor plan with brand new cabinets, sink, light fixtures and appliances! One bedroom with 1 full bath and a large garage that can easily fit 2 cars plus a HUGE man cave with a separate entrance that can be used as a recreational room or great for storage!! Huge fenced in back yard to entertain! Minutes from tons of restaurants and shopping on Randall road and to top it off 2 minutes away from Indian Trail Beach!!! Perfect for a first time home owner! Come and check it out! Move in ready!!!
